2017年4月9日[[棕枝主日|棕枝主日]]，在埃及北部的[[尼罗河三角洲|尼罗河三角洲]]城市[[坦塔|坦塔]]的圣乔治教堂與[[亞歷山大港|亞歷山大港]]的主要教堂[[科普特正教会圣马可主教座堂_(亚历山大港)|科普特正教会圣马可主教座堂]]发生两起自杀式爆炸。

造成至少45人遇難<ref name="CNN 10 April state of emergency">{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/04/10/middleeast/egypt-church-explosion/|title=Egypt Cabinet OKs state of emergency after Palm Sunday church bombings|authors=Joe Sterling, Sarah Sirgany and Ian Lee|work=CNN|date=2017-04-10|accessdate=2017-04-13|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226074841/https://www.cnn.com/2017/04/10/middleeast/egypt-church-explosion/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，126人受傷。在襲擊之後，[[埃及總統|埃及總統]][[阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西|阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西]]召開了國家安全委員會，宣布埃及進入三個月[[緊急狀態|緊急狀態]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/04/egypt-declares-state-emergency-church-bombings-170409192209801.html|title=Egypt declares state of emergency after church bombings|work=Al Jazeera|accessdate=2017-04-13|archive-date=2020-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614103001/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/04/egypt-declares-state-emergency-church-bombings-170409192209801.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[伊斯蘭國西奈省|伊斯蘭國西奈省]]在網絡上聲稱對這些攻擊負責。

== 背景 ==
2017年2月，[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]呼籲對[[基督徒|基督徒]]進行攻擊<ref name=":1">{{cite web |language=en |url=https://www.memri.org/reports/isis-egypt-openly-betting-bigotry-winning-strategy |title=ISIS Egypt Is Openly Betting On Bigotry As A Winning Strategy |last=Fernandez |first=Alberto M. |date=2017-02-22 |number=MEMRI Daily Brief No.120 |website=MEMRI |publisher= |access-date= |quote= |archive-date=2017-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012035354/https://www.memri.org/reports/isis-egypt-openly-betting-bigotry-winning-strategy |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[西奈半島動亂|西奈半島動亂]]導致越來越多基督徒逃離家園<ref>{{Cite web|language=en|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2017/02/25/Copts-flee-Sinai-after-suspected-ISIS-attacks-.html|title=Copts flee Sinai after suspected ISIS attacks|last=|first=|date=2017-04-09|website=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618052602/http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2017/02/25/Copts-flee-Sinai-after-suspected-ISIS-attacks-.html|archive-date=2018-06-18|dead-url=no|access-date=}}</ref>。

== 爆炸 ==
在2017年4月9日的[[棕枝主日|棕枝主日]]，第一起恐怖攻擊發生在坦塔的聖喬治教堂，造成27死78傷。幾小時後，第二起恐怖攻擊發生在亞歷山大港的[[科普特正教會聖馬可主教座堂_(亞歷山大港)|科普特正教會聖馬可主教座堂]]，造成17死48傷<ref name="chinatimes">{{Cite web|language=zh-Hant|url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170410000795-260408|title=埃及恐攻44死 進入3個月緊急狀態|date=2017-04-09|publisher=[[中國時報|中國時報]]|accessdate=2017-04-09|archive-date=2019-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019135327/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170410000795-260408|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃及教堂一位爆炸傷患回憶道：「我坐在前排，突然間一片黑暗，完全不知道發生什麼事。幾秒鐘後，我站起來，看到四周到處都是屍體」<ref name="pts">{{Cite news|language=zh-Hant|url=http://news.pts.org.tw/article/355092|title=埃及教堂爆炸44死百傷 IS宣稱犯案|date=2017-04-10|work=[[公共電視文化事業基金會|公共電視文化事業基金會]]|accessdate=2017-04-11|archive-date=2017-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170416164429/http://news.pts.org.tw/article/355092|dead-url=no}}</ref>。民營電視台播出的畫面顯示，聖喬治教堂內的白色牆壁上遍布血跡<ref name="udn">{{Cite news|language=zh-Hant|url=https://udn.com/news/story/5/2393424|title=埃及兩起教堂爆炸案 死亡人數增至共44人|date=2017-04-10|work=[[聯合新聞網|聯合新聞網]]|accessdate=2017-04-11|archive-date=2019-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190727192925/https://udn.com/news/story/5/2393424|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃及內政部表示，[[塞奧佐羅斯二世_(亞歷山大教宗)|塞奧佐羅斯二世]]當時正在聖馬可主教座堂主持基督苦難主日禮拜儀式，自殺炸彈客在門口遭警方攔下，隨即引爆炸彈，塞奧佐羅斯二世安然無恙。但教會人員說，塞奧佐羅斯二世在爆炸發生前即已離開教堂<ref name="udn"/>。

== 傷亡 ==
[[美联社|美联社]]报道，亚历山大港的爆炸造成17死48伤<ref name="AP killed 43"/>。CNN报道坦帕有28人死<ref name="CNN 10 April state of emergency"/>，而美联社报道有78人伤<ref name="AP killed 43"/>。两起袭击总造成45死<ref name="CNN 10 April state of emergency"/>，126伤<ref name="AP killed 43">{{cite web|last=Hendawi|first=Hamza|title=Palm Sunday church bombings in Egypt kill 43, wound dozens|work=AP News|date=2017-04-09|url=https://apnews.com/88b8fef3a96e433c902a303cd5db928e/Palm-Sunday-church-bombings-in-Egypt-kill-43,-wound-dozens|accessdate=2017-04-09|archive-date=2017-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170410051154/https://apnews.com/88b8fef3a96e433c902a303cd5db928e/Palm-Sunday-church-bombings-in-Egypt-kill-43,-wound-dozens|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 责任人 ==
[[伊斯蘭國西奈省|伊斯蘭國西奈省]]透過[[阿馬克新聞社|阿馬克新聞社]]網站聲稱對此次的恐怖攻擊事件負責<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/apr/09/egypt-coptic-church-bombing-death-toll-rises-tanta-cairo|title=Egypt: Isis claims responsibility for Coptic church bombings|last=Press|first=Associated|date=2017-04-09|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|accessdate=2017-04-09|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2018-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180120132249/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/apr/09/egypt-coptic-church-bombing-death-toll-rises-tanta-cairo|dead-url=no}}</ref>，聲明說：「伊斯蘭國派出的小組在坦塔與亞歷山大兩座教堂發動攻擊」<ref name="udn"/>。

== 反應 ==
=== 埃及國內 ===
埃及總統阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西召開了國家安全委員會，宣布埃及進入三個月緊急狀態，並派出軍隊在各地重要設施部署<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|language=de|url=http://www.spiegel.de/politik/ausland/aegypten-tote-bei-zweitem-anschlag-auf-koptische-christen-a-1142569.html|title=Terror in Ägypten: Zweiter Anschlag auf Christen – Präsident Sisi beruft Sicherheitsrat ein – SPIEGEL ONLINE – Politik|last=Germany|first=SPIEGEL ONLINE, Hamburg|website=SPIEGEL ONLINE|access-date=2017-04-09|archive-date=2018-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013131236/http://www.spiegel.de/politik/ausland/aegypten-tote-bei-zweitem-anschlag-auf-koptische-christen-a-1142569.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，警方在這段期間可逕行逮捕列管的可疑分子，即使沒有證據將其起訴送審，也可拘禁最多四十五天<ref name="udnM">{{Cite news|url=https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/2395424|title=武裝部隊派兵 埃及進入緊急狀態|date=2017-04-11|work=[[聯合新聞網|聯合財經網]]|accessdate=2017-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411141114/https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/2395424|archive-date=2017-04-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。塞西說，受傷的人員可以在軍事醫院接受醫療護理<ref name="NYT">{{cite news|language=en|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/09/world/middleeast/explosion-egypt-coptic-christian-church.html|title=ISIS Claims 2 Deadly Explosions at Egyptian Coptic Churches on Palm Sunday|publisher=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|date=2017-04-09|accessdate=2017-04-09|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127032443/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/09/world/middleeast/explosion-egypt-coptic-christian-church.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並表示：「我們已經發布一連串因應措施，並透過合法憲法程序，宣布埃及進入三個月緊急狀態，緊急狀態的實施是為了保護國家」<ref name="pts"/>。爆炸案發生後，[[西部省_(埃及)|西部省]]安全廳長遭埃及內政部撤換<ref name="udn"/>。

